<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en" class="geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable h-full antialiased"><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/><link rel="preload" href="/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.0r6juujl39pe6.woff2" as="font" crossorigin="" type="font/woff2"/><link rel="preload" href="/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.0wgildi0cnwt9.woff2" as="font" crossorigin="" type="font/woff2"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="/demo/hero-after.jpg"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="/demo/hero-before.jpg"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="/demo/case-faded-after.jpg"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="/demo/case-faded-before.jpg"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="/demo/case-bw-after.jpg"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="/demo/case-bw-before.jpg"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="/demo/case-damaged-after.jpg"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="/demo/case-damaged-before.jpg"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/_next/static/chunks/2kj2b6f3vdq0x.css" data-precedence="next"/><link rel="preload" as="script" fetchPriority="low" href="/_next/static/chunks/1jq4o6yq14o4c.js"/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/0atut6a2uuyid.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/3rxl-jt3pdxgx.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-38l7qwik-h828.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/158myu8e_yme3.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/3whwep12on06b.js" async=""></script><meta name="next-size-adjust" content=""/><title>PetPhotoRevive — Restore your pet&#x27;s old photos</title><meta name="description" content="Upload an old photo of your pet and see a free restored preview. Pay only if you love it."/><link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico" sizes="256x256" type="image/x-icon"/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js" noModule=""></script></head><body class="min-h-full flex flex-col"><div hidden=""><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class="flex min-h-screen flex-col bg-amber-50"><header class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl px-6 pt-10 text-center"><span class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-amber-800">PetPhotoRevive</span></header><main class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-4xl flex-1 flex-col gap-20 px-6 py-12"><section class="flex flex-col items-center gap-5 text-center"><h1 class="max-w-2xl text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-zinc-800 sm:text-5xl">Bring your pet&#x27;s old photos back to life</h1><p class="max-w-xl text-lg text-zinc-600">AI-powered restoration. See your free preview — pay only if you love it.</p><div class="mt-4 w-full max-w-2xl"><div class="relative w-full select-none overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 shadow-sm"><div class="relative aspect-[3/2] w-full bg-amber-100"><img src="/demo/hero-after.jpg" alt="After" class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover" draggable="false"/><div class="absolute inset-0 h-full overflow-hidden" style="width:50%"><img src="/demo/hero-before.jpg" alt="Before" class="h-full w-full max-w-none object-cover" style="width:200%" draggable="false"/></div><div class="absolute inset-y-0 w-0.5 bg-white/90 shadow" style="left:50%"></div><span class="absolute left-3 top-3 rounded-full bg-black/50 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white">Before</span><span class="absolute right-3 top-3 rounded-full bg-black/50 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white">After</span></div><input type="range" min="2" max="98" class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-3 mx-auto block w-[92%] accent-amber-700" aria-label="Drag to compare before and after" value="50"/></div><p class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-400">Real restoration of a 1900s postcard photograph. Drag to compare.</p></div></section><section class="grid items-start gap-8 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr]"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex flex-col gap-3"><label class="flex min-h-64 w-full cursor-pointer flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-amber-300 bg-white/70 p-8 text-center transition hover:border-amber-500 hover:bg-white"><input type="file" accept="image/jpeg,image/png,image/webp" class="hidden"/><span class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-700">Upload your pet&#x27;s old photo</span><span class="text-sm text-zinc-500">JPG, PNG or WEBP · up to 10MB</span><span class="mt-2 rounded-full bg-amber-800 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white">Choose a photo</span></label><p class="text-center text-sm text-zinc-500">Not sure? Just try — you&#x27;ll see your free preview first, and only pay if you love it.</p></div></div><aside class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-6"><h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700">Works best on:</h2><ul class="mt-3 space-y-2"><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-600"><span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-0.5 text-emerald-600">✓</span>Faded or yellowed old photos</li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-600"><span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-0.5 text-emerald-600">✓</span>Scratched or damaged prints</li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-600"><span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-0.5 text-emerald-600">✓</span>Low-resolution or grainy shots</li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-600"><span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-0.5 text-emerald-600">✓</span>Black &amp; white photos</li></ul><h2 class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700">Limited results on:</h2><ul class="mt-3 space-y-2"><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-500"><span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-0.5 text-zinc-400">✗</span>Heavily blurred / out-of-focus shots</li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-500"><span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-0.5 text-zinc-400">✗</span>Overexposed photos where details are washed out</li></ul></aside></section><section class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8"><div class="grid w-full gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3"><div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-6 text-center"><span class="mx-auto flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold text-white">1</span><h3 class="mt-3 font-semibold text-zinc-700">Upload</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">Add an old photo of your pet — faded, scratched or grainy.</p></div><div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-6 text-center"><span class="mx-auto flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold text-white">2</span><h3 class="mt-3 font-semibold text-zinc-700">Free preview</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">See the restored photo side by side with the original.</p></div><div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-6 text-center"><span class="mx-auto flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold text-white">3</span><h3 class="mt-3 font-semibold text-zinc-700">Download HD ($9)</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">Love it? Unlock the clean high-resolution version.</p></div></div><p class="text-base font-medium text-amber-900">You only pay if you love the result.</p></section><section class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-800">Every kind of old photo</h2><div class="grid w-full gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3"><figure class="flex flex-col gap-2"><div class="relative w-full select-none overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 shadow-sm"><div class="relative aspect-square w-full bg-amber-100"><img src="/demo/case-faded-after.jpg" alt="After" class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover" draggable="false"/><div class="absolute inset-0 h-full overflow-hidden" style="width:50%"><img src="/demo/case-faded-before.jpg" alt="Before" class="h-full w-full max-w-none object-cover" style="width:200%" draggable="false"/></div><div class="absolute inset-y-0 w-0.5 bg-white/90 shadow" style="left:50%"></div><span class="absolute left-3 top-3 rounded-full bg-black/50 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white">Before</s